Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.16,Title,Both,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,250)\pos(296.604,526.5)\bord4.5\c&HAC5FED&}Thời gian
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.16,Title,Both,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,250)\bord13.5\3c&H241C31&\pos(1691.321,542.25)}Tội lỗi\N Nguyên tổ
